platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: An endearing mix of two timeless franchises, this Angry Birds game cleverly melds the series’ physics-based puzzling with the retro flair of ’80s-era Transformers. Rovio fans will feel a new kind of euphoria as they charge through side-scrolling levels, blasting foes and toppling towers with strategically placed shots. Gamers smitten with Hasbro’s shape-shifting robots will be just as pleased, thanks to a gleefully synth-heavy soundtrack and huge roster of playable Autobirds and Deceptihogs.
